cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on the development and deployment of a customized deep learning-based video analytics system for surveillance cameras. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models and their training, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the security and safety applications of the system, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper mentions the use of embedded devices, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
